item.title: Introduction
item.description: Article goes here. For other options, put these in the front matter: description: “A description” other than the blog intro draft: true to not publish article yet showDate: true/false to enable/disable showing dates math: true to enable showing equations (katex) chordsheet: true to add chordsheet styelsheet For better seo you can set lastmod: 2020-4-11 after modifying an article, set lastmod to let google know that you have updated the article (SEO) sitemap: changefreq: “yearly” to let know how often article is changed priority: 0.
